Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I overslept and didn't have \Ntime, so it's omelet rice again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I don't need lunches anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.59,0:00:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the guys don't \Nbring their own lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.15,0:00:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone buys food at the school cafeteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, to get along with new friends, \NI don't need them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is such a pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, since I made it today, I \Nwant you to take it with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.07,0:00:36.32,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something nice will happen <3
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way I'd be able to eat \Nan omelet rice with a message
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,written on it in the classroom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 3 - Love and Flame
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be pretty spiritless today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is about how low my spirit is to \Nbegin with. Especially in the mornings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, for lunch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll splurge and go for the limited edition \Nbeef tongue curry to lift your spirits up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Limited edition? Will you make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I use my ability, a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have been waiting for you. Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I think you're better off \Nif you went to the hospital....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this? I'm pretty much used to this... \NI'm sorry to make you worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is an ability that is \Nway too incomplete after all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An outpouring of spices! \NThis is how curry should be!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I could meet your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Curry was something that \Nshould be spicy after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's medium spicy, but was this the \Nright spice level for you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The beef tongue also melts \Nin your mouth! It's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must really love curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I remember now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our helper is going to \Nmake another appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head over to the student council room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that guy always soaking wet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He can't use his ability unless he \Ngets soaking wet while fully clothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a cumbersome ability!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The ability is... channeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Channeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spiritualism. Allowing dead individuals \Nto possess them, like ITAKO shamans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not just a fraud, but someone who can \Nreally use it as a special ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One more... pyrokinesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think that someone has two abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to get moving to grab this person...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this is an ordinary road.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It means, the person is on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of a weekday? \NIs the person ditching school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, this road... this should be \Na narrow alley that is not that popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you asserting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:05:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, let's try heading \Nout to this location.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This place is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That person was pretty desperate \Nin passing through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This side is the only one \Nthat has no dust on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, whoever \Nit was ran through here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and bumped into this box or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, that means \Nthis person was being chased?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like an incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Another troublesome one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two new footprints. One has a \Nshort stride, and one is longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This totally indicates a girl \Nbeing chased by some adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that thing earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.61,0:06:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That filming session where an idol \Nwas being chased by a big guy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... that's right, \Nit was Yusa Nishimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Me, too...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yusarin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as I thought! It's \Nthe idol that Ayumi likes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's the vocalist for the band How \NLow Hello (nicknamed Haro-haro) –
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,an upcoming idol that can sing and dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were that big an idol \Notaku? That's such a turn-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When she was in 6th grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her career started from the achievement \Nof winning the grand prize...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...in the 14th reader-model audition for the \Nlow-teen fashion magazine "Petit Banana."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She debuted on that magazine \Nas their exclusive model!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The year after that, she landed a job as a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,regular member of the \N"Movement Morning!" show.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, she quit two years later to concentrate \Non high school entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She re-started her career in showbiz \Nafter advancing to high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, hold on, let's go back \Na bit to the issue at point!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that girl caused some issue with her \Nspecial ability, and became a fugitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say \Nthat for us to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her agency is Sea Rex Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be quicker \Nif we just called them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about someone in showbiz. \NThey won't tell us anything..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Found a suspicious target. \NGoing to chase him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otosaka, please do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The one that actually gets in pain is me, \Nso I rather you not use this tactic...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly why we have you on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do if the camcorder broke?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:07:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, who are YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if you spill it, we'll call \Nan ambulance for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you're headed \Nstraight to death, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was just offered a job...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that something you'd risk your \Nlife to protect the secrecy of?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for Yusa Nishimori!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Asked by who?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Taiyo TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know that far... that's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood! I had already \Ncalled for an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are just looking for a \Nwoman named Yusa Nishimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her nickname is Yusarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the reason why, but it's a fact \Nthat she's being chased,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we thought we'd help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You guys know Yusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a huge fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't break the flow of the \Nconversation every single time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching you the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NHow did you defeat that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With special abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is most likely something like \Nthe ability that Nishimori has.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you trust us, I believe \Nthat we can save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see... then, prove to me that \Nyou have the same power as her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the same power, but here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now do you believe us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... now, come with me. But \NI'm sure you'll be confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Things got slightly complicated. I \Nwant you guys to see for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive. it's a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to go so far to film this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This way. Don't be slowpokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How was it outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It actually is the real Yusarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have all the Haro-haro CDs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a turn-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It really is the girl I \Nsaw on TV back then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's with those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're just like Misa, and \Ncan use special abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Misa? So her real name wasn't Yusa but Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the complicated part.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right to trust them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They used their powers to \Ndefeat those other guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, can we ask her directly \Nwhat's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask something stupid, don't think \Nyou can get out of here unscathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on, you're being scary...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomori, be careful here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. I'm Tomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nice to meet you! I'm Yusa \NNishimori, nicknamed Yusarin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She calls herself Yusarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I \Nmeet an idol in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are so cute that it \Nfeels like someone created you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get that close, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, first off, please tell me your real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"My name is Yusa Kurobane!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your real name sounds more \Nfitting as a stage name...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I hear that often... But, \Nblack feathers (kurobane)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't sound too suitable for an \Nidol, so they renamed me to Nishimori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. So, Kurobane... there are \Ntimes that you are not Kurobane.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aware of that fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She is not aware of it.\N How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't asking you, bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, Kurobane, how is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you can call it sleepwalking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, I don't realize I fell asleep, \Nand when I wake up I'm somewhere else...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The doctors tell me that there \Nis a chance that I have a
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,multiple personality disorder...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:12:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not schizophrenia, \Nso please rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She has a special ability just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her power is to allow a dead \Nperson to possess her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that this power calls forth \Nthis Misa girl that you guys talk of?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it someone she knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's Yusa's sister who \Nwas older by a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She passed away six months \Nago from an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't go blabbing this and that \Nto someone stranger you just met!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, can it be that you're Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a cramped place... all you \Ngathered here? So annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a change in personality...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What an impressive ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Misa! Are you going \Nto burn us all to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That guy has no sense at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So she can't call the spirit forth on her \Nown will, and Misa actually controls it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Another ability that is somehow imperfect!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That means, she has an unparalleled \Nability to be possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Misa, who possesses Yusa, \Nhas the pyrokinetic ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is your relationship with these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're my buddies from back when \NI was alive and mischievous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the reason why your \Nlittle sister is being chased?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yusa accidentally brought this \Nhome on accident from some shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It belongs to one of the bigger-named \Nproducers at the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yusa accidentally read a \Ntext that was sent to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Using up company money, connections \Nto a dangerous crowd -
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,stuff that will get the guy under \Narrest if this was taken to the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you turn the power off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But it wasn't turned \Noff until yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then they probably know already that you're
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hiding somewhere in this area from the GPS.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you returned the smartphone \Nnow, you won't stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And even if you handed it to the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that would mean Kurobane sold \Noff that producer off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and make it impossible \Nto keep working in showbiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll burn it all \Ndown, TV station and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid? You do that, and \Nyour little sister will be arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell do you think you are, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you really want to send your little \Nsister off to juvenile hall or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That would be in bad sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down. You want to \Nsave your little sister, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we should help each other, and \Ninstead threaten this guy instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the chances of winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really good at creating plans for \Nthreatening others! Please trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've got good character. All \Nright, I'll do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like both of you to help as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If Misa says so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Right now... was I asleep again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired. It's all right. Have \Nsome roasted marshmallows and calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the marshmallows turned into \Nfreshly-roasted marshmallows!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have absolutely no clue how I should \Napproach Yusarin from now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're a scary guy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we should first head to \Na shop that sells work clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you will need fireproof clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You realized that you can't escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I really don't know the reason \Nwhy I'm being chased so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did Yusarin do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my smartphone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I return it, like, \Nis Yusarin still in a crisis?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens, there is no \Nfuture for you in this industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a future?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Such a person is more like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll take out one more of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What... what the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You probably thought that you cornered me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but you really didn't realize that it was \Nme cornering you. You really are senseless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you... are \Nyou really Yusa Nishimori?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'm Yusa Nishimori, \Nthe real Yusarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In order for me to succeed, I can \Nkill anyone, just like those guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It does hurt after all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is cumbersome. I'll \Nget rid of them at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'm gonna wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can bury you into the \Nshadows at any point we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! I give up! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give this back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, there is no next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eradicate you, no ifs, ands, or buts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, you helped us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He believed that everything that happened \Njust now was done by Yusa alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That producer will no longer \Nbe able to go against Yusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not settled in stone quite yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I'd like you to transfer into \NHoshinoumi Academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and do everything alongside us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just like how I explained earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,she'd get caught by the scientists and \Nher days as a guinea pig will begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She will never be able to return to \Nnormal life ever again, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The condo next to our academy will be the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nsafest place in all of Japan for Kurobane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a life-saving story for Yusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go ahead and do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.... then, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If Yusa's powers disappear... \Nwe can never meet Misa again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I wanted to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's already dead first \Nand foremost, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it more abnormal that you were \Nable to see her for all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sho, everything is like what she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In reality, she no longer exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this is time for us \Nto say goodbye to Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't we decide on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let me tell her how I truly feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how to put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This has to be when I can't \Nthink of anything to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sho, did you have the hots for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Misa, I loved you. It's \Nembarrassing to say, but I was in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you passed away before \NI could tell you that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it was an accident while we were \Nriding one motorcycle together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was okay with just small wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I was the one that killed you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I made you harbor such immense feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I was the one that sought \Nsuch dangerous thrills.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I reaped what I had sewn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry. That's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sho, forget about me, and starting \Ntomorrow, live your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't keep dragging the dead into your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, your life would get screwed up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you won't be happy in the future, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you really are a troublesome boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sho...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will walk down my own path \Nthat you are not a part of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sever off my feelings for you... \Nand that is how I will live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Both of you, \Nlead a very happy life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See ya! Thank you for everything until now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was absolutely the most fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, it was a really long day...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're really late! If you're going to \Nbe this late, I wanted you to call me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As for you... you were up this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eating dinner together is a rule passed \Ndown the Otosaka house for generations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was busy again today doing \Nwork for the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you say that, I can't say anything back...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what is the home-made food tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am most satisfied with the \Nmeat-sauce spaghetti tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otosaka house Secret! Pizza sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Haro-haro again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really is the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who and who are you talking of?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:21:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean "Yusa Nishimori," \Nand the actual person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The actual person? Can it be that \Nyou have gotten to know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh crap... but they didn't tell \Nme to stay quiet about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.04,0:22:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I guess I can tell her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.62,0:22:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, she's transferring into my academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.62,0:22:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me way too jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would Ayu be able to meet her or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the possibility is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.63,0:22:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, start by wiping your nosebleed clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is something amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.84,0:22:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on... you're getting \Ntoo excited about this...{\i0}
